node.text: Su país queda del otro lado, dejen de llorar.
un lugar único, con una energía diferente…. 🫶🏾🖤
Great visual but what is the name of the audio?

People cry about literally everything nowadays man! Yes they got a little scared from a drone? And? Theyre still alive and healthy. If anything they got to practice their survival instincts and keep them sharp. Relax people! Smoke something special if u have to itll chill you out a bit
